B2_U_res_structure.statement:
Let R(z) subset Fib_w(z) and U_res(z) = number of distinct monic length-w prefixes u of Lambda_U for residual/lex sides U of S in R(z). Then:
(i) U_res(z) <= |R(z)|;
(ii) for each u, the number of e-subsets with monic prefix u is <= floor(n/e);
(iii) N_can_prim(z) <= U_res(z) * M_m^{max} (v5 routing);
(iv) if M_m^{max} <= 1 then N_can_prim(z) <= U_res(z).
